                      int m,

        Creates a new Newton.CalculationJob with given arguments.
        Only a part of the image from yMin to yMax is calculated by this job, meaning only a part od the data array is written on.
        Parameters:
        reMin - Minimum value of the real part.
        reMax - Maximum value of the real part.
        imMin - Minimum value of the imaginary part.
        imMax - Maximum value of the imaginary part.
        width - Raster width used for image visualization.
        height - Raster height used for image visualization.
        yMin - Minimal y-axis value that is calculated by this job.
        yMax - Maximal y-axis value that is calculated by this job.
        m - Maximum number of iterations.
        data - Array with calculated results that need to be visualized.
